N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 97.2 - Definitions

State Regulations

For purposes of this Part, a credit union organization shall
be defined as any organization established primarily to serve the needs of its
member State and Federal credit unions and whose business relates to the daily
operations of the credit unions it serves. Notes
